# Figma → Flutter mapping

## Inputs by phase

| Phase | Inputs |
|-------|--------|
| **layout** | `cleaned.json`, `figma.png`, user context |
| **plan** | `layout_observation.json`, `cleaned.json`, `assets.manifest.json` |
| **build** | `build_plan.json` v2 |

## Auto Layout → plan (`widget_tree.layout`)

| Figma | Plan intent |
|-------|-------------|
| HORIZONTAL | `row` → `Row` |
| VERTICAL | `column` → `Column` |
| Wrap | `wrap` → `Wrap` |
| Fill container | `expanded` / `flexible` |
| Absolute | `stack` + `positioned` |
| Overflow / long lists | `scroll_model` + `ListView` / slivers |

## Layout `ui_role` → plan `widget` (examples)

| `ui_role` | Typical `widget` |
|-----------|------------------|
| `button` | `FilledButton`, `TextButton`, `InkWell`+container |
| `text_field` | `TextField` |
| `label` | `Text` |
| `icon` | `SvgPicture`, `Icon` |
| `image` | `Image.asset` |
| `list_item` | extract → `StatelessWidget` |
| `chrome` | `SafeArea`, status placeholders |
| `decorative` | non-interactive `Container` / `SvgPicture` |

## Fidelity (per `widget_tree` node / extract)

`fidelity`: `native` (default) | `image_bake` | `stub` — an **honest downgrade** beats crooked native layout.

| Value | When | Requirements |
|-------|------|--------------|
| `native` | Auto Layout / text / standard controls rebuild faithfully | — |
| `image_bake` | Complex vector art, gradients, illustrations that native widgets cannot match | `assets[]` binding for the same `figma_id`; **forbidden** on interactive nodes (bake the visual as a child, keep a native tap layer) |
| `stub` | Content out of scope (maps, webview, video) | `plan_notes` entry + contract `out_of_scope` or coverage note |

Downgrades are recorded in the plan — never decided silently in build.

## plan → build

`build_plan.json` v2 sections:

- `screen_architecture` — shell and scroll
- `widget_tree` — node map
- `extracted_widgets`, `theme_bindings`, `assets`, `interactions`
- `files_to_create` — build checklist

**build** implements verbatim; no geometry outside plan + `cleaned.json`.
